    "description": "Run this collection from top to bottom with the Ecommerce Local environment selected. The first request seeds runtime variables used by later requests.\n\nFlow order: bootstrap auth -> admin setup -> seller setup -> products -> cart -> orders -> user account -> seller reports -> payments -> marketing -> admin ops -> notifications.",
